faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"講多少少<br />\n好多人唔識點樣杯葛中資公司/國產貨<br />\n下面我比少少例子大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">衣：</span><br />\nUniqlo（記得睇tag檢查係咪中國製）<br />\nMuji（同上，中國製請放低）<br />\nAd-lib（本地品牌，少貴，同樣請檢查tag）<br />\n其他大牌子，例如Nike、Adidas、The North Face嗰啲自己睇tag，有國產有非國產）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">食：</span><br />\n卡樂B（香港製造）<br />\n出前一丁（睇碗蓋，有港產有國產）<br />\n果粒橙（樽身招紙寫到明「香港製造」，其他太古product請睇樽身）<br />\n益力多（睇樽身，有港產有國產）<br />\n明治奶（泰國製，既然所謂設香港廠房嘅維x都係用中國奶喺香港將啲奶倒落個盒到，不如飲外國奶）<br />\n<br />\n大家參考下<br />\n如有錯誤請指正<br />\nanyway買任何嘢之前同我檢查產地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f27a281ab058e8e558fa1140c13ea448b376a7","tid":1551451,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e819e77da07edd0a7fbc3defd093beebeb66e33a","tid":1551451,"uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ea22400d6b2484f7a84b0351d49709a4d5934b02","tid":1551451,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"2間大學 2個多人嘅ocamp<br />\n完左camp都食富臨<br />\n我想問<br />\n其實係咪我太上心？<br />\n其實係咪得我嬲？<br />\n定其實得我有睇新聞？<br />\n<br />\n真係唔怪得廢中廢老屌我地大學生剩係識搞亂個社會無9用<br />\n從眾打卡比嬲嬲咪叻<br />\n杯葛紅色閪店<br />\n支持港產product<br />\n咁簡單都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n好無力<br />\n可唔可以比我喺到圍個爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:56:02.000Z","msg":"你做得好啱<br />\n我都一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5cLhOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5cLhOi.jpg&h=63614906&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:22:37.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"a2f6a8ec0a0f0884174687c9e978b184159a1336","tid":1551451,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco